" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa79596915e1766fa0b06d86351d242c4bd8dc2","tid":409311,"uid":128192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"上年本人fd仔表示唔好理佢地 做好自己 識朋友識個想讀書嘅。完"},{"pid":"82a81fed8f4a84e4f6a6bd42f3c9b826c19a9d12","tid":409311,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要令班垃圾讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫佢地返工好過啦</blockquote><br />\n一係老豆老母好有錢。一係就申請援助，唔撚洗自己比。再唔係就立心不良特登害鳩人。"},{"pid":"fa5df4af1aeac641057b3e1673a47e5569b609e1","tid":409311,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年本人fd仔表示唔好理佢地 做好自己 識朋友識個想讀書嘅。完</blockquote><br />\n明白。我都唔想曬左錢同時間。"},{"pid":"22504a4df1de1c87cc4ba1fb80bfbb7bb921bd7b","tid":409311,"uid":128563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:13:30.000Z","msg":"其實hd啲英文都係學實用文，寫下信寫下report咁，而啲人都係一撚樣係咁起度傾偈同鳩笑嘈到個lecturer屌佢哋先識收下皮"},{"pid":"f91206f43e91ac492ab9f5d1b6639dbad39c881b","tid":409311,"uid":38548,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:16:40.000Z","msg":"ive果名<br />\n<br />\n蘋果定火龍果?"}]}